<paragraph blockId="8.[132,681,1016,1296]" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">
<emphasis box="[132,230,1017,1040]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">Discussão:</emphasis>
As quatro duplas de manchas pubescentes elitrais e a conformação do espinho apical caracterizam a espécie. Duas outras espécies brasileiras aproximam- -se morfologicamente a 
<taxonomicName authority="Curletti &amp; Migliore, 2014" authorityName="Curletti &amp; Migliore" authorityYear="2014" box="[379,477,1112,1136]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="femina" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[379,477,1112,1136]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">A. femina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[485,567,1112,1135]" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
: 
<taxonomicName authority="Kerremans, 1897" authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1897" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inflatus">
<emphasis box="[577,681,1112,1136]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">A. inflatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="KERREMANS, C." box="[132,308,1144,1168]" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" pagination="1 - 146" refId="ref15132" refString="KERREMANS, C. 1897. Contribution a l'etude de la faune intertropicale Americaine. Voyages de M. E. Gounelle au Bresil. Buprestides. Memoires de la Societe entomologique de Belgique, 6: 1 - 146." type="journal article" year="1897">Kerremans, 1897</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
do 
<collectingRegion box="[347,450,1144,1168]" country="Brazil" name="Amazonas" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">Amazonas</collectingRegion>
e 
<taxonomicName authority="Kerremans" authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1897" box="[473,680,1144,1168]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="unicus">
<emphasis box="[473,564,1144,1168]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">A. unicus</emphasis>
Kerremans
</taxonomicName>
de 
<collectingRegion box="[164,294,1176,1200]" country="Brazil" name="Pernambuco" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">Pernambuco</collectingRegion>
. 
<taxonomicName authority="Curletti &amp; Migliore, 2014" authorityName="Curletti &amp; Migliore" authorityYear="2014" box="[304,401,1176,1200]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="femina" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[304,401,1176,1200]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">A. femina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[409,487,1176,1199]" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
separa-se de 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kerremans" authorityYear="1897" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inflatus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">A. inflatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
pela diferente ditribuição da pubescência elitral; da segunda principalmente pela disposição diferente do espinho apical, na metade e não na margem externa.
</paragraph>
